Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Strong dollar hits jobs
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xkc5
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 24 Mar 1985
Jobs hit as strong dollar means US exports are too pricey for world markets. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.